rokeColor=#c9a72a;fontColor=#57450e;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="662" y="0" width="222" height="108" as="geometry"/></mxCell></object><object label="No pure-time discount&lt;br&gt;(astronomical stakes)&lt;br&gt;[1+2+3+4]&lt;br&gt;→ AI safety (Redwood Research)&lt;br&gt;▼ 23 more worldviews" tooltip="&lt;b&gt;parochial + far_away_humans + animals_somewhat + future_humans_matter_with_discounting + no_discounting_future_humans&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Accept that future people count exactly as much as present ones (Ord, MacAskill) and Bostrom&#x27;s astronomical-waste argument follows: the expected size of the future dwarfs the present, and reducing existential risk dominates everything measurable. This is the stop Ajeya Cotra&#x27;s near-termist deliberately gets off before. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 3 future_humans_matter_with_discounting → 4 no_discounting_future_humans" link="https://viewer.diagrams.net/?lightbox=1&amp;nav=1&amp;chrome=0#Uhttps%3A%2F%2Fraw.githubusercontent.com%2Fmorganrivers%2Ftrain_to_crazy_town%2Fmain%2Fdiagram%2Ftrain_tree__w1_2_3_4.drawio" id="w1_2_3_4"><mxCell style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fontSize=11;fillColor=#f6e0c0;strokeColor=#c9932a;fontColor=#5a3f10;dashed=1;dashPattern=8 4;strokeWidth=3;fontStyle=1;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="474" y="239" width="244" height="108" as="geometry"/></mxCell></object><object label="Animals matter a lot&lt;br&gt;(RP welfare ranges)&lt;br&gt;[1+2+3+5]&lt;br&gt;→ Shrimp Welfare Project&lt;br&gt;(Bob Fischer, Brian Tomasik)" tooltip="&lt;b&gt;parochial + far_away_humans + animals_somewhat + future_humans_matter_with_discounting + animals_matter_a_lot&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Replace the neuron-count proxy with Rethink Priorities&#x27; welfare-range estimates (Fischer et al.) and count invertebrates — shrimp, insects, and the ~10^19 soil animals. Under RP medians a chicken&#x27;s welfare range is a third of a human&#x27;s, not a fiftieth, and wild/soil invertebrates carry significant aggregate (nematode) weight, so invertebrate work dominates. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 3 future_humans_matter_with_discounting → 5 animals_matter_a_lot" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJzFWGtz08gS%2FStdKahrZyNbtgmQUPmQhwMUgc2Ns8veS6gwlsbWrCWNmBlFMWz47ffMSPIrdgifLlUURurpPt19%2BjH6vhXyEctjcyxDvrW%2F1W7TwcEBXSomUjKSAsW%2BTfGjSOkq7%2FqdZ1RIFYc3ghdUdK67173rXWpoIzPabdqjVylUHGqdJ5kRMqUggqZ98iljSgaRYLFV1NnrUodGTF2zgk2vozxhqa5fdImlImGxvtYy4UXETP2mR6Pc5IpXB64TZgxX14Uw0XUodCDz1Ih0XIvvzhRVguw6lsYh7LMgIjaHKTQxOp%2BaCL9HIuYE9%2BevdZuMhcHCUO%2BQ4oiZSLkmqZwyxT14xxIOG0LjuYl46fi%2FNBCngdPxigKZZFJbgDMBnE1DDo14JLTTpg1LQxbLlFOCpMQt%2BjKLef%2Fmi4Vqj%2FPbjAcGB29YnHOSI6dhnp6WU3bEtaFhPqXcmrEHNV90bJ8GkRJJRh95jHRwOlfyb%2BgtT7%2Fuf%2BhfHF72T2g4pTFPuWKGt7JpzQUeCrMUpm283KFUmhKMjSQ0OV1%2FpAFXxrqcSAUWzCKmS9kyHCzLYsF1iwbTpBXLcSoVEtj4nu3uULa3e9d0uly29vyndPz2lZMccsPKp5mSQzYUsTAAMpTW7dAS%2BZO%2FQ53PLTplgZGwCV9LVRDIbA5Ss0NaErfEkGqMzPU%2FFSeHZ%2F9pP%2FlMQx7LAny1Z12G%2BS1%2Bx1Mch25E1emC7TAPTJkLZI%2BDo3C%2F5OxJxU86uO%2FbPvW45790Lpa%2Fn981iaxKnPSMSDj9RgEzTBslM%2Bi2fE5z5rhrKcuUV5qp6NC4YInm0%2FYAAU7ph%2F%2B0PVV0o%2BmDVGHEck0%2FOq1d%2B%2FAV6vAAGaO6fppVvk6EAg%2BIj0b2H9hYiEwGyjA1RVhSVEIg8HuHjvqnv1%2F0y%2Bw6DQUX48jW4%2BZs1mSevaMikmCoKaSnBVLnFJWZtrKfqpOfawYyuK%2FAbE%2BOvISNU2HykNPR75f9Y6RzmgxlLAKX1xuupk6bTUujWaXUciZl8dRACuSOXI1AqWZJFvOwVTaK0uuRGNsAV2U6VhW5bKOEC1rmKkBVC1uTtqPYGsLD7J0wQcTTcy6h8Q2PMx6ec%2FWHDtczwW%2F5uxUR%2FJYj%2FIISVGk85AjpaxTLCXBv1OF3Zkr8zoqWY5tnriydcxYfsXTypyNNqStPxQi6Gn4LKgBh%2Baw1OoP%2FsHvb9CDybWp0yKOf4yprPjIm0%2FvtdlEUrbG44QUUtpCYtrBnUlcKLG4bHkSpCPAL1ThGi9HtgOnIMwrFOEK3uUrH4ZITG%2BLnP5sH0O%2Fe%2FQREJAuv4B6676QNIniBEnYYsHYgtfHKIoI8hoZe88hzjR7QWDJ6DLbenCF%2Bt7MGG5opAEzR1BTPMGJ4rnQkshYmUBtWRPIYKwsM6u6uGAFD8qQ1c4LFRuVCJy4WmHFGt1%2Befv04%2BHqzd8jPZDFmf6fr%2FEbVBlJl0s4VL0DNMTFOtQftHnaFYMLRi0wU%2Fwxtp9WtsD578ctA%2B8N%2FT%2FVft3I0HHydDA%2FF5Qag2g1KZNkNSi8rB6WnPbeMYALoIvsp0K7vV0hfPAPHfhlsM