d Pearce)" tooltip="&lt;b&gt;parochial + far_away_humans + animals_somewhat + future_humans_matter_with_discounting + animals_matter_a_lot + suffering_focused&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Asymmetry: averting intense suffering takes priority over creating happiness. Factory farming, malaria and the worst wild-animal conditions weigh up; speculative future-flourishing bets weigh down. Arises most naturally from taking animal suffering seriously, so it requires animals_somewhat. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 3 future_humans_matter_with_discounting → 5 animals_matter_a_lot → 6 suffering_focused" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJzFWWtT28gS%2FStdVFLXZpEtm0ACKT7wMAkVkmWBTfbekHLG0tietaRRZkYIJ0t%2B%2Bz0zkvzCJuZ%2BuVSlIiRN9%2Bme091nxI%2BNkPdZFpljGfKN%2FY1mkw4ODuhaMZGQkRQo9n2Mizyhm6ztt15QLlUU3gqeU97qtrvb3Z3uLtW0kSnt1u3imwRGDrXO4tQImVAwhK198illSgZDwSJrqrXXphb1meqynI27wyxmia4etIklImaR7moZ83zITPVkm%2FqZyRQvF3RjZgxX3VyYYTcUOpBZYkQyqF7fmRgqX2TdSE6M7ZLO%2Bn2usKDbl0GmeejAd1gwJDaNQGhidDE2Q1z3RcQJuZk%2B1k0yFiELQ71FiiOhIuGapHLGFPcQOIs53AuN%2B2bIi5z8SyOYJHA2XlMg41Rqi33yAtYmIYdF3BLaWdOGJSGLZMIpxo5FDfo62ZDO7VcL1S7ndykPDBbesijjJPvOwnTvGs7YEdeGetmYMuvGLtR8NrB9uhoqEaf0iUfYKU4XSv4Nu8XqN50PncvD684J9cY04AlXzPBGOq6IwkNh5tK0iYdblCD%2FDozNJCw5W38mAVfGhhxLBYJMMqaLd4t0sDSNBNcNuhrHjUgOEqmwt7Uf6c4WpXs793Vny%2B3Wnv%2Bcjs9euzd73LDibqpkj%2FVEJAyA9KQNO7Qs%2F%2BxvUetLg05ZYCR8ItbCFF5I7R4kZou0JG6JIdUAO9f5nJ8cnv%2B7%2BewL9Xgkc1DZrnU7zO9wHY2xHLaRVWcLvsMsMMVeYPc46Ivw%2B5HMsGqIjT8p%2BUsHDwNE%2FTT8Vy5Me%2Fnqvk7kyAWbiCHnYjCEbVSb4sxVwBDZsjzUVLuWMdNi9Jo%2BIiD7rO23fSRrwv4LJQDdjJd7bjVapePdxk7pmN8ZxWbcslvsnzWNmHkCGk1sr3ZfVPLjUW9zbxK2vd4t%2FadY6RkRc%2FqNAmaYNkqmSKut8iRjrmxttTLlFW7KSqhdsljzcfMK3Erop%2F%2B8OVZ0q%2BmDVOGQZZp%2Btho79uZrdKcDkJWqrlIvqXoiFEqAOMILXOgzpEhRLUyNwYgETSAQuN6io87p75edgtjOQpE1JGI1kas6njyjfCiRVZNLT4uw7FMFye27n8uVX6riYwhfoag92fdiNkiEyUJOR79fd47B5HHck5EIHKWxcWNnzTKyVi%2FZbMslYdHY4C3U9dC1BxjVLE4jHjaKHllE3RcDm%2BCyQw1UWVd2gCAEDX4HaGjCtiPbTG37wM30nT