4PSZNVaKVKsQHS%2BFtE0AnNfIVB8ZnOEHTBQh5yl0rMNjDUCzlrctjjZRdCjYzskaqngc39ipwXg4Tawny9Toh8EOch36XLtRNrDtEKZxqVSvlzbcJHZpeXS3GnrdVo2dD%2BjBkroy%2B2dl80mcM3c2aWGG43uFfVNWL391h1p36y1%2Fe03Vwn8ZrNG7FYsgd1cwE03G4sRsqWoHFjjySw2C0L%2FvwuJwzNv53%2BB1AaM7AfGSqZTY%2F%2F9cXOGe3EKqPa7%2BxHjIdgLZhZx3zH2AOr9t%2B%2BpTYcV3O6tsWIO%2BcJk8TdCvmDo78b8Aun2xqleOuFsmPMZ4MXhYh2lenOzsyzay0AuLG7OrV4V49vAln92nEvuhYnC2vc3l3JhGbqFxc251Y9F9wkDAqFTApKmRjk2oJ9p1DgRcT1H2CWjhNvu0VjvGmjOLDwWb9WqZmS8LZ3WydFx8XPcUn4uLYz3aaNpXXyc%2BmqukF%2B%2Fus8KJXbrrZV67NZ7dzu1K8yzzFuIXPPehLxbQdBVB9wWu7NSF9AZZAlT4WiOSHdVBliw9DDu0x5TZCsViPPLdyC%2FWDVSN%2BM9SDhtWsp%2BLdS84f5jG%2FTBpFE25w368df1X3TdmoN004RO79vfGPbqrv7Z%2F1KJnIulv1JcvHl7PpMwu6UqsNqnX%2F9UAW0kgMJ%2BOp%2F74QM72Dfmd79M127%2BA2PdSUU%3D" id="w1_2_3_5_6_11"><mxCell style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fontSize=11;fillColor=#c9b3dd;strokeColor=#4a2a78;fontColor=#201040;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="1652" y="1434" width="200" height="108" as="geometry"/></mxCell></object><object label="Meat-eater problem&lt;br&gt;(saved humans eat animals)&lt;br&gt;[1+2+3+5+7]&lt;br&gt;→ Shrimp Welfare Project&lt;br&gt;(Michael Dickens, Vasco Grilo)" tooltip="&lt;b&gt;parochial + far_away_humans + animals_somewhat + future_humans_matter_with_discounting + animals_matter_a_lot + meat_eater_problem&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;The meat-eater problem: a dollar of human global health also buys decades of that person&#x27;s meat consumption, and factory farming it causes suffering the animal circle now counts. Each present-human org is charged an additive penalty — farmed-animal life-years caused per human DALY, times the suffering per factory-farmed life-year, times the animal&#x27;s welfare range. Under a heavy animal welfare range the penalty can exceed the human benefit, so saving human lives looks net-harmful. Only bites once animals count, so it requires animals_somewhat; and it is a near-term human-vs-animal get-off point, not combined with astronomical-stakes longtermism (no_discounting_future_humans), where x-risk dominates and the meat bookkeeping is moot. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 3 future_humans_matter_with_discounting → 5 animals_matter_a_lot → 7 meat_eater_problem" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJzFWGtT28gS%2FStdVFLXJsiW7RAWUnzgYZJUSJYL7GbvDSlnLI3tWUsaZWaEcLLkt98zI8kvbHA%2BXaoohDTTfbr79GPmx1bIByyLzIkM%2BdbBVrNJh4eHdK2YSMhIChT7PsFDntBN1vZbLymXKgpvBc8pb%2FXavU5vt7dHNW1kSnt1u%2FkmgZAjrbM4NUImFIwg64B8SpmSwUiwyIpq7bepRQOmeixnk94oi1miqw9tYomIWaR7WsY8HzFTfenQIDOZ4uWGXsyM4aqXCzPqhUIHMkuMSIbV8t2poHIh60VyKmyPYs5MD7%2F4kirZj3js0HdZMCI2M0FoYnQxMSM8D0TECc6ZfdZNMhYiC0O9Q4rDoyLhmqRywhT3YDmLObQIjfdmxAun%2FEvDmiRwMl5TIONUagt%2BugB7k5BDIl4J7aRpw5KQRTLhFCNkUYO%2BTiPSvf1qodrt%2FC7lgcHGWxZlnOTASZgFr%2BGEHXNtqJ9NKLNq7EbN5w07oKuREnFKn3iEUHG6UPJvyC12v%2Bl%2B7F4eXXdPqT%2BhIU%2B4giMb6aRiCg%2BFWXDTNj7uUIIAODDWk5DkZP2RBFwZa3IsFRgy9Zgu1hbuYGkaCa4bdDWJG5EcJlIhuLUf6e4Opfu793Uny0Vr339OJ%2B9eu5V9bljx1gaZ9UUkDID0pTU7tDT%2F7O9Q60uDzlhgJHTC1kIUFqQ2BonZIS2JW2JINUTkup%2Fz06Pz%2FzSffaE%2Bj2QOLtu9LsL8Ds%2FRBNshG151sqA7zAJTxIJb6iUa5hd8Pi25S4cPbTugDvf835yJxfOr%2BzqRFYmdnhExpxcUMMO0UTKFbMv1JGOOu5ayTHmFmpIOtUsWaz5pXsHBCf30nzcnim41fZQqHLFM089WY9e%2BfI0cPUTEqMqtehmvU6HAA%2BKDgf0DHXOeSUEZpiZwS4JMCASed%2Bi4e%2Fb7ZbeIrpOQczEc2VxdH82KzNNvlI8kGGpy6WmB0DlBRaTt2s%2Flzi8VAxnMV2C2JwdezIaJMFnI6fj36%2B4JwjmJ%2BzISgYvrLVcTJ82GpVYvQ2o5k7BoYrAK5B65HIFQzeI04mGjKBSF1QMxtA4u03SoSnLZMgoTtMxUgKwWNidtRbE5hJfpe2GCEU8uuITEtzxKeXjB1R86XM0Ev%2BHvlkTwG47wc0KQpVGfw6VvkCynwL1Wht%2BaCvFbS1JObJy5snTOWHTMkvGfjjSFrCwRA8iq%2BQ2IAITFvVbpFP7j5m3To8i3qdYij57GVeT8yJhUHzSbeZ43huKW5xDYQGCawu5JXCqwqGl4MEpEgCdk4xAlRjcDpkeeUUjGAarNTTIMF4xY4z%2F%2F5cyBfvv%2BCRAjmXs591B9x00QwQuUsM2ANQOpjVckEdajaegVrzxX6AGNxYNNsHVmDPHbrRXYUEwBYIKipniKFsMzpUcibaADNaFFxJtomWNQe3dJCRiSxY2pESwyKhM6dr5AjzO6%2BdvZt09X3273j%2Fi5zIfs72SV3cjaQKpU2r7iBcg5JoaJ9iDdwxwRjDlqkRlFT6FtNdol1pd7vwy02%2F%2F3RP91Jwf9q2%2Fj%2FpG4XgNUu0aJKLtG6aVFo%2FS05wYVdACdp08Cbft%2BiXTvJTj2y2DjoRanx