problem: a dollar of human global health also buys decades of that person&#x27;s meat consumption, and factory farming it causes suffering the animal circle now counts. Each present-human org is charged an additive penalty — farmed-animal life-years caused per human DALY, times the suffering per factory-farmed life-year, times the animal&#x27;s welfare range. Under a heavy animal welfare range the penalty can exceed the human benefit, so saving human lives looks net-harmful. Only bites once animals count, so it requires animals_somewhat; and it is a near-term human-vs-animal get-off point, not combined with astronomical-stakes longtermism (no_discounting_future_humans), where x-risk dominates and the meat bookkeeping is moot. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 3 future_humans_matter_with_discounting → 7 meat_eater_problem" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJzFWGtT28gS%2FStdVFLXJsiWDIRAig88TJIKyXKBXfbekCJjaWzPWtIoMyOEk2V%2F%2Bz0zkvzCBvLpUkVh5JnuM92nu8%2Fo51rE%2ByyPzZGM%2BNreWrtN%2B%2Fv7dKmYSMlIChX7McaHIqXrvOMHW1RIFUe3ghdUBDedm82bHWpoIzPaadqt1ylMHGidJ5kRMqVwCEt75FPGlAyHgsXWULDboYD6TN2wgo1vhnnCUl1%2F0SGWioTF%2BkbLhBdDZupvNqmfm1zxasNNwozh6qYQZngTCR3KPDUiHdTLdyjhzNzgF4syJXsxTxy%2BLguHxKYghSZGZ2MzxOe%2BiDnh8NOvdZuMBcGiSG%2BQ4oiYSLkmqZwxxT2cjSUcXoTGczPk5bH%2FpYE3DZ2NtxTKJJPawpsswN404rCIR0I7a9qwNGKxTDklSEncom%2BTiHdvv1modju%2Fy3hosPGWxTkn2XcWpslpOWOHXBvq5WPKrRu7UfPZg%2B3RJWy9t8HkdMrZIOflxnfdz93zg8vuMfXGNOApV4hhKxvXJOCRMHMRWseXG5RKU%2BKwQYQlZ%2Bv3NOTK2NMmUiH9k2Dpcm0ZCZZlseC6RRfjpBXLQSoVKND4mW1vULa7fd90tlyidv2XdPThrVvZ44aVT21%2BWU%2FEwgBIT9oTR5bBX%2FwNCr626ISFRsInU7w0hQWZDX9qNkhL4pYTUg2QtO6X4vjg9D%2FtF1%2Bpx2NZgKh2r0suv8PneIztsI2AOlvwHeWhKdPALetSjeOXZD2uiEn7D8%2B2R5vc89%2B4I5afX983iaxJ7PSMSDi9opAZpo2SGWxbxqc5c7S1bGXKK91UTGics0TzcfsCAU7pH%2F9le6zoVtNnqaIhyzX9E7S27cO3KMB9ZIzqwmlW%2BToWCtQi3u%2FbP%2FAxE5lMoTDVGGFJUQShwOcNOuye%2FHbeLbPrLBRcDIa2EFdns%2Bbx5DsqhhLkNIX0tEDqnKEy03btl2rn15qBDMdXILUn%2B17CBqkwecTp8LfL7hHSOU56Mhahy%2Bs